name: UWaveOscillatorCameraShakePattern
doc: A camera shake that uses oscillations to move the camera.

LocationAmplitudeMultiplier: Amplitude multiplier for all location oscillation
LocationFrequencyMultiplier: Frequency multiplier for all location oscillation
RotationAmplitudeMultiplier: Amplitude multiplier for all rotation oscillation
RotationFrequencyMultiplier: Frequency multiplier for all rotation oscillation
